Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <enum-fields> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT enum-fields (enum-field*)>
 <!ATTLIST enum-fields
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
